"tropical-monsoon", "origin": "South Africa. Cultivated globally for medicinal and ornamental purposes.", "traits": "Large branching shrub, 1.8-2.4m tall. Multi-headed with narrow tooth-edged leaves in rosettes.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "Available in India from medicinal plant nurseries and botanical gardens. Growing popularity for medicinal gardens.", "sort_order": 9}], "variety_count": 17}'::jsonb,
