ands, Limgroup. Primarily for white asparagus production.", "traits": "Thick vibrant green spears when grown green, fine straight stems, firm tips, thick with well closed tips, mid to late season.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "High productivity, reliable yields. All-male (100%). Good half of production is 20-28mm class. Royal Horticultural Society Award of Garden Merit.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "", "sort_order": 20}, {"name": "Mondeo F1", "slug": "mondeo-f1", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "humid-subtropical", "origin": "Germany. All-male hybrid.", "traits": "Green spears, early season cropping.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "Great yields. All-male (100%).", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "", "sort_order": 21}, {"name": "Thielim F1", "slug": "thielim-f1", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "humid-subtropical", "origin": "Netherlands, Limgroup. Recent introduction.", "traits": "White asparagus production specialist, average earliness.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "Good production capacity. All-male (100%).", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "European suppliers - Lindflora (Netherlands), Dutch nurseries. Import required.", "sort_order": 22}, {"name": "Viking KB3", "slug": "viking-kb3", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "humid-subtropical", "origin": "Mary Washington-type hybrid, newer variety.", "traits": "Green spears with purple tips, sturdy variety, 20-25cm length.", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "High yields, many stalks. Mix of male/female plants. Popular commercial option.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "Limited availability, specialty suppliers, may require searching international sources.", "sort_order": 23}, {"name": "Alternative: Asparagus racemosus (Shatavari)", "slug": "alternative-asparagus-racemosus-shatavari", "lineage_type": "indigenous", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "", "traits": "", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "5-6 tonnes dry roots per acre (medicinal use)", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "Widely available in Kerala - local nurseries, Kerala Agricultural University, Ayurvedic medicinal plant nurseries, horticulture departments", "sort_order": 0}], "variety_count": 25}'::jsonb,
